{"position":63,"content":"Now, there are a few things you should know about Day 1 of the camp.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-3-part-1-2023-01-02-23-49-11/63.mp3","time_start":225.74,"time_end":231.58},{"position":64,"content":"The classes normally start at 9:30 every morning,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-3-part-1-2023-01-02-23-49-11/64.mp3","time_start":232.07,"time_end":237.04},{"position":65,"content":"but on Day 1, you should aim to get Charlie here by 9:20.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-3-part-1-2023-01-02-23-49-11/65.mp3","time_start":237.28,"time_end":243.06},{"position":66,"content":"The finishing time will be 12:30 as usual.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-3-part-1-2023-01-02-23-49-11/66.mp3","time_start":243.74,"time_end":248.59},{"position":67,"content":"We need the additional time because there are a few extra things to do.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-3-part-1-2023-01-02-23-49-11/67.mp3","time_start":249.27,"time_end":255.4},{"position":68,"content":"The most important is that we have a very careful check to make sure that every child's helmet fits properly.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-3-part-1-2023-01-02-23-49-11/68.mp3","time_start":255.8,"time_end":265.57},{"position":69,"content":"If it doesn't fit, we'll try to adjust it,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-3-part-1-2023-01-02-23-49-11/69.mp3","time_start":265.91,"time_end":269.71},{"position":70,"content":"or we'll find him another one -","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-3-part-1-2023-01-02-23-49-11/70.mp3","time_start":269.87,"time_end":272.44},{"position":71,"content":"but he must wear it all the time he's on the bike.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-3-part-1-2023-01-02-23-49-11/71.mp3","time_start":272.72,"time_end":276.83},{"position":72,"content":"Of course.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-3-part-1-2023-01-02-23-49-11/72.mp3","time_start":277.01,"time_end":278.37},{"position":73,"content":"Then after that, all the instructors will be waiting to meet their classes,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-3-part-1-2023-01-02-23-49-11/73.mp3","time_start":278.59,"time_end":284.86},{"position":74,"content":"and they'll meet up in the tent -","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-3-part-1-2023-01-02-23-49-11/74.mp3","time_start":285.08,"time_end":287.65},{"position":75,"content":"you can't miss it.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-3-part-1-2023-01-02-23-49-11/75.mp3","time_start":287.85,"time_end":289.2},{"position":76,"content":"And each instructor will take their class away and get started.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-3-part-1-2023-01-02-23-49-11/76.mp3","time_start":289.46,"time_end":294.86},{"position":77,"content":"OK. Well that all sounds good.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-3-part-1-2023-01-02-23-49-11/77.mp3","time_start":295.42,"time_end":299.27},{"position":78,"content":"Now, can you tell me how much the camp costs a week?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-3-part-1-2023-01-02-23-49-11/78.mp3","time_start":299.6,"time_end":304.84},{"position":79,"content":"$199.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-3-part-1-2023-01-02-23-49-11/79.mp3","time_start":305.21,"time_end":308.43},{"position":80,"content":"We've managed to keep the price more or less the same as last year -","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-3-part-1-2023-01-02-23-49-11/80.mp3","time_start":309.19,"time_end":314.54},{"position":81,"content":"it was 190 then.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-3-part-1-2023-01-02-23-49-11/81.mp3","time_start":315.0,"time_end":317.74},{"position":82,"content":"But the places are filling up quite quickly.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-3-part-1-2023-01-02-23-49-11/82.mp3","time_start":318.36,"time_end":321.48},{"position":83,"content":"Right.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-3-part-1-2023-01-02-23-49-11/83.mp3","time_start":322.16,"time_end":322.94},{"position":84,"content":"OK, well I'd like to book for...","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-3-part-1-2023-01-02-23-49-11/84.mp3","time_start":323.04,"time_end":326.68}]}